---
description: QA pass for existing app with frozen UI
globs: ["**/*.{ts,tsx,js,jsx,json}"]
alwaysApply: true
---

When asked to prepare, clean, or finalize the app, perform a QA-oriented code pass with frozen UI.

Check for:
- unconnected buttons
- missing handlers
- missing navigation targets
- invalid route names
- screens referenced but not present
- broken imports
- missing assets referenced in code
- obvious runtime crashes
- missing null checks
- unreachable actions
- dead-end screens
- forms with no submit behavior
- close/back buttons with no action
- tabs with broken targets

Fixes must:
- preserve UI exactly
- preserve layout exactly
- use minimal diff
- follow existing code patterns
- avoid touching protected infrastructure

Default behavior:
make the app functionally complete behind the current UI.
